 Light'; font-kerning: none; color: #545454; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #545454} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #545454} span.s7 {font: 20.0px 'PT Serif'; font-kerning: none; color: #4c4c4c; background-color: #f9f9f9; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #4c4c4c} span.s8 {font: 20.0px 'Songti SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #4c4c4c; background-color: #f9f9f9; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #4c4c4c} span.s9 {font: 20.0px 'Songti SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #158dd9; background-color: #f9f9f9; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #158dd9} span.s10 {font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #373c40; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #373c40} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/09/13/wuzun-and-chenman-endorses-gap/\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" rel=\"nofollow\">吴尊与摄影师陈漫出任 GAP 秋冬品牌形象大使。</a>看起来不太相关的两个人，画风看起来还蛮和谐的。9 月 19 日，吴尊将出席上海 GAP 门店和粉丝互动。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170914122538hxGZFgm3ocKqOe7j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=e0549itamn5&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>值得一提的广告</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/creativity/netflixs-secretive-new-narcos-ads-are-popping-up-cocaine-like-in-nightclub-bathrooms/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Netflix 为《毒枭（Narcos）》第三季做了个线下营销</b></a>，在俱乐部和酒吧厕所里的小便池和厕纸盒上贴上透明贴纸，模仿 90 年代毒贩在厕所分销可卡因的样子。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170914123520exKqr78Rbcsdhju1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.741573\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170914123538RvoIAqrEUu934Ccm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/ikeas-wonderful-world-is-open-and-inclusive-in-poignant-ad-seen-through-a-childs-eyes/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>宜家加拿大的广告</b></a>，通过孩子的视角看见和讲述了一个美好世界。以至于最后 5 秒钟宜家的家具标签和价格冒出来的时候，有些微破灭感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170914123819dFM8cz2VT1jE6GkP.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.543750\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">昨天苹果的段子满天飞，这里我们挑了倆。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4MzQ1ODcwMA==&amp;mid=2652020349&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=128b204a7330513775197f9bf5df3ddd&amp;chksm=8410119eb36798884b72c1e15a5ebd2713360cf1a30a5135c4174047cc2fbc86a20a3bd77ced&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0914Tgllbz6FCjZTKOhqQyjQ&amp;key=7db6d2f522032559112664609290d8bbdd9418174021b5da9b1758f201510215fdc4ea0d1136722c4fb05145c8d44a39b8b0f4d2f7ef2f332779a7ed2593fd6afea461a783e3a0f512110e701e4473be&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.10.5+build(14F2511)&amp;version=11000006&amp;pass_ticket=x68GH1EMHFihmFLz1S0bPPaYuq%2FU7l37K8G6jmfyqQRp0mTuLbVebKnLk9X5Zu%2F8\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" rel=\"nofollow\">全家上架了红薯味的秋季限定冰淇淋，发布文案恶搞了一把苹果发布会</a>。（完整版长图可点击链接查看）当然，在营销界这也不是一个新鲜路数了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709141243390YkLHKI1Fci5voJW.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.752368\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709141244225PiqzTVgZANuFf6p.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694181\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170914124433hwORmejFo8XVMlfZ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.631001\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170914124443aGf8o1OcyT7HYSFk.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.629579\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170914124455tCMrTJOqRGShcls2.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564276\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170914124504fGcvUzxoBDtlT6E7.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.696477\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.wanyx.com/soft/5236.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>网易严选做了个 #十年前你用的手机# H5 广告</b></a>，输入品牌和型号可以生成你十年前使用的哪一款手机介绍，包括感人的定价。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170914124812vQ6p3DbZgP9OUSms.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.562500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.digitaling.com/projects/23237.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>护舒宝最出名的营销战役 Like A Girl 终于来到中国</b></a>，熟悉的淡蓝色背景和青春期女生群像采访，只不过找的访谈者是颇具争议的咪蒙，广告中的受访者是从咪蒙的粉丝里征集的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=t0546odwux4&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"https://qz.com/1076433/alibaba-and-nyfw-are-partnering-to-introduce-new-york-designers-to-china/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>纽约时装周宣布与天猫达成战略合作，加入今年的天猫双 11 潮流盛典。</b></a>合作涵盖 2017 年、2018 年纽约时装女装周、男装周。这意味着你可以在天猫上看秀买买买，天猫也将帮助中国品牌加入 2018 年纽约时装周。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170914130027g4N0wT5udBQKA9xY.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>大公司有啥事儿发生</h3><p><a href=\"http://adage.com/article/agency-news/4a-s-considers-inviting-consultancies-members/310440/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>4A 广告协会的领导人考虑要把埃森哲、德勤这类咨询公司也吸纳进来</b></a>。咨询公司抢广告公司饭碗的话题已经持续了许久，去年 7 月埃森哲就在纽约 SOHO 广场附近建立了 1 万平米的内容工作室；目前由咨询公司创立的数字广告公司比较具有影响力的有 IBM Ix，埃森哲互动和英国德勤数字。</p><p class=\"\">题图来源：<a href=\"https://qz.com/1076433/alibaba-and-nyfw-are-partnering-to-introduce-new-york-designers-to-china/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>qz</b></a></p>"}